org.apache.zookeeper.server

类 ZooKeeperServerConf

  • java.lang.Object
    • org.apache.zookeeper.server.ZooKeeperServerConf

  • public class ZooKeeperServerConf
extends Object
    Configuration data for a ZooKeeperServer. This class is immutable.
